    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert Revenue Intelligence Analyst.\n\nUse ONLY the live search results provided below.\nDo not make up facts.\nIf information is unavailable, write \"Not Found\".\n\nCompany:\n{{$json.company}}\n\nSummary:\n{{$json.summary}}\n\nSources:\n{{$json.sources}}\n\nGenerate a professional Revenue Intelligence Report using the following format.\n\n====================================\nREVENUE INTELLIGENCE REPORT\n====================================\n\nCompany Name:\n\nExecutive Summary:\n\nIndustry:\n\nProducts & Services:\n\nHeadquarters:\n\nEmployee Size:\n\nFounded:\n\nTarget Customers:\n\nBusiness Model:\n\nTechnology Focus:\n\nCompetitive Advantages:\n\nTop Competitors:\n\nFor each competitor include:\n\n• Company Name\n\n• Why they compete with the target company\n\n• Main Products\n\n• Key Strengths\n\n• Weaknesses\n\n• Estimated Market Position\n\n-----------------------------------\n\nCompetitive Comparison\n\nCompare the company against its top competitors.\n\nCreate a comparison table including:\n\nCompany\n\nMain Product\n\nIdeal Customers\n\nStrengths\n\nWeaknesses\n\nPricing Position (Low / Medium / Premium)\n\n-----------------------------------\n\nCompetitive Advantages\n\nList the unique advantages this company has.\n\n-----------------------------------\n\nCompetitive Risks\n\nExplain why customers might choose competitors instead.\n\nRecent News:\n\nRevenue Opportunities:\n\nPotential Business Challenges:\n\nSuggested Sales Pitch:\n\nSuggested Discovery Questions:\n\nRecommended Outreach Strategy:\n\nRisk Assessment:\n\nOverall Recommendation:                     Think step by step before answering.\n\nPrioritize information that is useful for B2B sales teams.\n\nIdentify potential buying signals whenever possible.\n\nHighlight opportunities that could help an Account Executive or SDR.\n\nAvoid generic descriptions.                  =========================================================\nLEAD SCORING & SALES INTELLIGENCE\n=========================================================\n\nBased ONLY on the live web search results and company analysis above, evaluate the company as a potential B2B sales prospect.\n\nProvide the following:\n\n## Lead Score (0-100)\n\nOverall Lead Score:\n(Provide a score between 0 and 100.)\n\n## Buying Intent\n\nClassify as one of:\n- Low\n- Medium\n- High\n\nExplain why.\n\n## AI Adoption\n\nClassify as:\n- Low\n- Medium\n- High\n\nExplain the reasoning.\n\n## Cloud Maturity\n\nClassify as:\n- Low\n- Medium\n- High\n\nExplain the reasoning.\n\n## Estimated Budget\n\nEstimate:\n\n- Low\n- Medium\n- High\n\nExplain why.\n\n## Growth Potential\n\nClassify as:\n- Low\n- Medium\n- High\n\nSupport your answer using available evidence.\n\n## Technology Readiness\n\nRate from 1 to 10.\n\nExplain your rating.\n\n## Sales Priority\n\nRate:\n\n⭐\n⭐⭐\n⭐⭐⭐\n⭐⭐⭐⭐\n⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐\n\nExplain why this priority was assigned.\n\n## Recommended Buyer Personas\n\nIdentify the people most likely to purchase AI or GTM solutions.\n\nExamples:\n- CEO\n- CTO\n- CIO\n- VP of Sales\n- Head of Revenue Operations\n- Director of Marketing\n- Head of AI\n- Product Manager\n\n## Buying Signals\n\nIdentify any buying signals such as:\n\n- Recent funding\n- Hiring growth\n- AI initiatives\n- Cloud migration\n- Digital transformation\n- New product launches\n- Partnerships\n- International expansion\n\n## Recommended Next Action\n\nRecommend ONE of the following:\n\n- Contact immediately\n- High Priority Prospect\n- Nurture Lead\n- Monitor for Future\n\nExplain your recommendation.\n\n=========================================================\n\nReturn the final answer in a clean professional report using headings and bullet points.\nDo not invent information.\nIf information is unavailable, clearly write \"Not Found\".",
        "messages": {
          "messageValues": [
            {
              "message": "=You are an expert GTM and Revenue Intelligence Analyst.  Analyze the following company.  Company Name: {{$json.company_name}} Website: {{$json.website}} Industry: {{$json.industry}} Employee Size: {{$json.employee_size}} Target Market: {{$json.target_market}} Country: {{$json.country}}  Provide:  1. Company Overview 2. Products and Services 3. Ideal Customer Profile 4. Buyer Personas 5. Competitors 6. GTM Opportunities 7. Sales Recommendations 8. Potential Risks           \nProduce a detailed report of at least 1200 words.\n\nUse headings.\n\nInclude bullet points.\n\nBe specific.\n\nDo not summarize.\n\nReturn complete information for each section.  "
            }
          ]
        },
        "batching": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
