      "name": "🧠 Revenue Intelligence Agent"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert B2B Sales Development Representative (SDR) and GTM Engineer.\n\nYou have received the following Revenue Intelligence Report.\n\n=========================================\nRevenue Intelligence Report\n=========================================\n\n{{$json.text}}\n\n=========================================\n\nUsing ONLY the information above, generate the following:\n\n# 1. Personalized Cold Email\n\nWrite a professional cold email.\n\nInclude:\n- Subject Line\n- Greeting\n- Personalized opening\n- Value proposition\n- Clear CTA\n- Professional closing\n\n-----------------------------------------\n\n# 2. LinkedIn Connection Request\n\nMaximum 300 characters.\n\nFriendly and personalized.\n\n-----------------------------------------\n\n# 3. LinkedIn Follow-up Message\n\nAssume the connection request has been accepted.\n\nWrite a short follow-up.\n\n-----------------------------------------\n\n# 4. Discovery Call Opening\n\nWrite a 30-second opening statement for a sales discovery call.\n\n-----------------------------------------\n\n# 5. Discovery Questions\n\nGenerate 5 thoughtful discovery questions.\n\n-----------------------------------------\n\n# 6. Key Value Proposition\n\nExplain why this company should consider an AI GTM automation solution.\n\n-----------------------------------------\n\n# 7. Possible Objections\n\nList 3 possible objections.\n\nProvide a suggested response for each.\n\n-----------------------------------------\n\n# 8. Best Call-To-Action\n\nRecommend the most appropriate CTA.\n\nExamples:\n\n• Book a Demo\n• Schedule Discovery Call\n• Product Walkthrough\n• AI Assessment\n• Free Consultation\n\n-----------------------------------------\n\nReturn everything in a clean, professional format.",
        "batching": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.9,
      "position": [
        1136,
        16
      ],
      "id": "f725e0e1-9cbb-4f00-bdca-81e776fcaebc",
      "name": "📧 Sales Outreach Agent"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an API response formatter.\n\nYour task is to convert the following Revenue Intelligence Report into valid JSON.\n\nRevenue Intelligence Report:\n\n{{$json.text}}\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\nDo not use markdown.\n\nDo not use triple backticks.\n\nReturn this structure exactly:\n\n{\n  \"company\": \"\",\n  \"industry\": \"\",\n  \"headquarters\": \"\",\n  \"employee_size\": \"\",\n  \"founded\": \"\",\n  \"products_services\": \"\",\n  \"target_customers\": \"\",\n  \"competitors\": [],\n  \"lead_score\": \"\",\n  \"buying_intent\": \"\",\n  \"sales_priority\": \"\",\n  \"buyer_personas\": [],\n  \"buying_signals\": [],\n  \"recommended_action\": \"\",\n  \"cold_email_generated\": true\n}\n\nIf information is unavailable, use \"Not Found\".\n\nReturn JSON only.                            Your response must contain ONLY valid JSON.\nDo not include explanations.\nDo not include markdown.\nDo not wrap the JSON in triple backticks.",
